{"tid":2017122,"cid":37,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人租樓超過3年？ [2]","createTime":"2020-05-15T02:14:44.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-17T06:48:19.000Z","uid":103921,"like":13,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"27f5101b859dcf1e434f49989be9370092ae731d","tid":2017122,"uid":103921,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T02:14:44.000Z","msg":"見無人開[2]. 以下開放討論<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有冇人租樓超過3年？<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1065299\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1065299</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: violet;\"><strong>精選回覆:</strong></span><br />\n條數唔應該咁計喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n1. 你租樓唔洗首期, 你應該係租樓期間用呢舊錢去投資cover甚至賺返俾左出去既租.<br />\n2. 買樓要俾稅, 經紀費, 律師費, 呢度最少要十幾萬冇左. 買完仲要俾管理費, 地租, 差餉. 呢度除返埋你當每月最少要出千幾蚊.<br />\n3. 如果唔係full pay要按揭, 要俾利息. 分三十年都要幾十萬甚至過百萬.<br />\n<br />\n總結就係租樓又好買樓又好, 你要係香港/地球生存就係要付出. 冇話租樓就蝕買樓唔會蝕. 最後最後就係如果你係AA就收手啦.<br />\n<br />\n利伸: 租樓一年, 有舊錢投資已賺返D租金<br />\n==================================================================<br />\n同你一樣！ 租左接近一年<br />\n<br />\n計個自己租間屋租金回報扣埋管理費差餉得2% 回報<br />\n所以無興趣買樓<br />\n<br />\n好多投資野唔只呢個回報，我認我係淡友，覺得樓市唔跌都唔會有好大升幅"},{"pid":"2f2b3a1a964c4a7eac67cfd3de431f935e34192b","tid":2017122,"uid":10905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T04:29:44.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"01831378d4a4ab44b7456fe9bca068494a862964","tid":2017122,"uid":210707,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T07:06:50.000Z","msg":"又bin <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc69ef2f716f1995e5299f869eb82edbcde0243a","tid":2017122,"uid":10637,"like":3,"dislike":4,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T07:12:04.000Z","msg":"依年有邊個投資係可以cover個租<br />\n真係真股神<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n買樓就無依個問題"},{"pid":"bde9762fa346f4c0315a5d3b49ebc32461f7623f","tid":2017122,"uid":104804,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T07:14:05.000Z","msg":"租樓一年, 有舊錢投資已賺返D租金<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b70e771cc2e507a5fab119152efe8bfd1b962a61","tid":2017122,"uid":152225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T07:15:51.000Z","msg":"樓主有其他投資強。當然無問題"},{"pid":"ae74832564819f01167ad40806665bda486271ca","tid":2017122,"uid":222543,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"bde9762fa346f4c0315a5d3b49ebc32461f7623f","tid":2017122,"uid":104804,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T07:14:05.000Z","msg":"租樓一年, 有舊錢投資已賺返D租金<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T07:20:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n當你15萬租一年 一年可以keep投資賺到15萬無蝕<br />\n然後你有咁嘅實都仍然唔上車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"921f32d41ea79a9fbfccde633774fc0bddcc1871","tid":2017122,"uid":222543,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"ae74832564819f01167ad40806665bda486271ca","tid":2017122,"uid":222543,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"bde9762fa346f4c0315a5d3b49ebc32461f7623f","tid":2017122,"uid":104804,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-15